duties_responsibilities.duty: Cultivate new and existing client business development opportunities for the Supply Chain function.
Lead, mentor and grow consultants and actively participate in the performance management process.
Lead engagements by communicating and reporting project status to C-level executives and supply chain management.
Create effective go-to-market strategies while driving the development/enhancement of West Monroe’s Supply Chain methodologies, best practices, and approaches to client delivery.
Manage and enable new go-to-market offering lifecycle from ideation to launch/client delivery in collaboration with industry teams.
